## DrawingAttributeSet

* *Attribute types*: `drawing`, `fill`, `line`, `image`, `shape`, `geometry`, `connector`, `chart`
* *Operations*: [addStyle](#addStyle), [insertDrawing](#insertdrawing), [setDrawingAttributes](#setdrawingattributes), [setAttributes](#setattributes)

Contains attributes for `drawing` style sheets and drawing objects, in the following format:

|Property|Data Type|Default Value|Description|
|--------|---------|-------------|-----------|
|`styleId`|String||Identifier of a drawing style sheet inserted with an [addStyle](#addStyle) operation.|
|`drawing`|[DrawingAttributes](#drawingattributes)|{}|Drawing formatting attributes.|
|`fill`|[DrawingFillAttributes](#drawingfillattributes)|{}|Additional fill formatting attributes for the entire drawing object.|
|`line`|[DrawingLineAttributes](#drawinglineattributes)|{}|Additional line formatting attributes for the entire drawing object.|
|`image`|[ImageAttributes](#imageattributes)|{}|Additional image attributes, only used for image and OLE objects.|
|`shape`|[ShapeAttributes](#shapeattributes)|{}|Additional formatting attributes for auto-shapes and text frames.|
|`geometry`|[GeometryAttributes](#geometryattributes)|{}|Additional geometry attributes for auto-shapes and text frames.|
|`connector`|[ConnectorAttributes](#connectorattributes)|{}|Additional connector attributes for connector shapes.|
|`chart`|[ChartAttributes](#chartattributes)|{}|Additional chart formatting attributes, only used for chart objects.|

